::Halucigen::
Halucigen stopped running.
'He wants to see me..."
Halucigen walked back the way he had come and looked the other bot in 
the eyes.
"You wanted to see me....well look into my eyes then."
Should this other bot look into the eyes of Halucigen he would begin 
to see his worst nightmare as if it were real. It would seem as if he 
was in a new world.
